Program: Outlook
Title: 23/08/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00wvmw8
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 24 Aug 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, we hear from a Malian journalist attacked for standing up against the Islamists who took over his hometown. Also on the programme, the American woman who worships both as a Christian and a Muslim and a blind expert in echolocation skills, who started by instinct and now teaches his method to blind people around the world. Show less